704859f-b.title: Brooklyn: Henry Street - 9th Street (West)
704859f-b.text:

where modern low cost housing units will shortly rise. The
apartrent house seen is at the S.W. corner. Beyond same is the
Larsen Bakinm Co.
View No. 2 emplasises the easterly side of this thoroums
